PAUL RULE SYSTEM (Cursor)

1.  Purpose
    A.  Point Cursor at the repository’s rule system under
        `paul/`.

2.  Prompt handling
    A.  Read and apply `paul/rule/prompt.txt` to each prompt.
    B.  Update `paul/chat_log.txt` for each prompt.
    C.  Maintain files in `paul/spec/` when prompts change
        primary app features outside `paul/`.

3.  Rule file formatting
    A.  When editing any file in `paul/`, apply
        `paul/rule/outline.txt`.

